 "text": "goodness, is known to be"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Also"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A thing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K,) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a mark, trace,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "track,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "by which one guides himself,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "is guided,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K, TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to the road,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "way;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, TA;) as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Eul~aAmapN", "text_ar": "عُلَّامَةٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalomN", "text_ar": "عَلْمٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (K: [in several copies of which, in all as far as I know,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "waAlEalomu", "text_ar": "وَالعَلْمُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is here put in the place of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "wAlEalomi", "text_ar": "والعَلْمِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; whereby"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlEalomu", "text_ar": "العَلْمُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is made to be syn. with"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlEaAlamu", "text_ar": "العَالَمُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": but accord. to SM, it is syn. with"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlmaEolamu", "text_ar": "المَعْلَمُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", as is shown by what here follows:]) and hence a reading in the Kur [xliii. 61], ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "waA_in~ahu laEalomN", "text_ar": "وَاـِنَّهُ لَعَلْمٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lils~aAEapi", "text_ar": "لِلسَّاعَةِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "And verily he,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e. Jesus, by his appearing, and descending to t